creator: Onze Stad App
descriptionHtml:
De Kortenberg City-App is een messenger waarmee je met de lokale overheid, handelaars, zorgverstrekkers en verenigingen kan communiceren. Koppel u met uw lokale handelaars, verenigingen, zorgverstrekkers en u zal kunnen genieten van digitale communicatie om zaken te bestellen, reserveren, ..., nieuws te ontvangen.
Kortom, de Kortenberg City-App is uw mobiele toegangspoort tot alle diensten in uw gemeente.
descriptionShort: The mobile platform for your region
title: Kortenberg

creator: Onze Stad App
descriptionHtml:
The Kortenberg City-App is a messenger for communicating with the local government, merchants, care institutions and associations.
Connect with your local merchants, associations and care institutions and you will be able to enjoy digital communication to order products, make reservations, receive news, ...
In short, the Kortenberg City-App is your mobile gateway to all services in your region.
